com.bmc.arsys.api

Class DirectAssociation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmc.arsys.api.ObjectBase
      • com.bmc.arsys.api.Association
        • com.bmc.arsys.api.DirectAssociation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IARPersistentObject, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class DirectAssociation
extends Association
implements Serializable, Cloneable
    The DirectAssociation class represents a type of association which encapsulates each mapping for fields involved in a primarykey - foreign key relationship. The datatypes and properties for the fields in the mapping should match.
